  <h1>Monads in Haskell, explained without the jargon</h1>
  <div class="artmeta"><span>By Coldwast</span><span>Updated Jun 14, 2026</span><span>8 min read</span><span class="tag">#haskell</span><span class="tag">#monads</span><span class="tag">#concepts</span></div>
